    "body": "I think `Transferred` can be declared as `event Transferred ( address from, address too)` . And then we can emit it in multiple functions as:\r\n\r\n- In Constructor: `emit Transferred(address(0),  _owner)`\r\n- In `renounceOwnership` : `emit Transferred( _owner, address(0))`\r\n- In `_transferOwnership` : `emit Transferred( _owner,  newOwner)`",
